{"tid":186561,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【妓院版Uber】華裔母女檔賣淫集團落網！生意橫跨美29州","createTime":"2017-04-04T09:45:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-04T21:53:32.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7af8f368ad44ac34e8876fc4738a8a5a8e15c985","tid":186561,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T09:45:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170404/large/1491291576_4270.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170404%2Flarge%2F1491291576_4270.jpg&h=88c8d98d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2017年04月04日<br />\n多州警方聯合公布，上月成功搗破一個跨州賣淫集團，經過多番追查後，發現主腦竟是藏身在洛杉磯爾灣市一對華裔母女以及2名同黨。她們旗下管理的賣淫事業橫跨美國29州，極有組織有如「妓院版Uber」。<br />\n<br />\n加州爾灣市居民、23歲的吳芳耀（FangYao Wu，音譯) 、48歲的景虹(Hong NMN Jing，音譯)二人為母女關係；另外同黨有奧蘭治縣奇諾崗（Chino Hills）居民、49歲的黃索菲亞(Sophia Wang Navas，音譯）以及28歲的蔣東舟（Dongzhou Jiang，音譯）共4名華裔嫌犯被捕。明尼蘇達州檢控官將起訴4人敲詐勒索、教唆賣淫及色情販賣等多項罪名。<br />\n檢察官Peter Orput表示，該犯罪集團內部分工明確，總部設在加州爾灣，賣淫活動則大多發生在明尼蘇達州到北達科他州。其中於去年6月1日，景虹曾因在爾灣開設妓院，在一次警方臥底行動中被逮捕。<br />\n他又指，吳耀芳、<a href=\"http://景虹及黃索菲亞過去兩年通過Backpage.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E6%99%AF%E8%99%B9%E5%8F%8A%E9%BB%83%E7%B4%A2%E8%8F%B2%E4%BA%9E%E9%81%8E%E5%8E%BB%E5%85%A9%E5%B9%B4%E9%80%9A%E9%81%8EBackpage.com&d=N89%2BOK2GKuUyahfhaKnAsr%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=49d6bf1b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">景虹及黃索菲亞過去兩年通過Backpage.com</a>上發布賣淫信息招攬顧客，顧客會得到一個地址，只要上門便可獲得性服務，就好似Uber版的色情販賣。<br />\n受害者大多是不會英語的中國或韓國女性年齡界乎32歲到49歲，部份受害人還需交出護照。如果不遵守規定，他們就受到驅逐出境的威脅。她們亦頻繁被集團首腦在多個賣淫場所間轉運，讓她們難以在同一個地方建立關係或求救。<br />\n警方指，受害者被規定每天必須掙夠800美元（約6,240港元），否則將遭開除甚至被遣返，這些女性每天工作12至14個小時，每筆性交易，賣淫首腦從中收取50美元（約390港元）提成。這些女性頻繁被羞辱、強姦及被顧客搶劫，蔣東舟被捕後表示，「這是她們生活的一部份，賣淫是一個高風險高回報的工作。」<br />\n警方從4名疑犯的手機及電腦中確認該組織發布的信息超過18,200條，目前三名在加州被拘捕的疑犯正在等待被遣送到明尼蘇達州受審。<br />\n[url]<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170404/56520959\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170404%2F56520959&d=N89%2BOK2GKuUyahfhaKnAsr%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=a19ba401\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170404%2F56520959&h=f7d1eb58\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170404/56520959</a><br />\n[/url]"},{"pid":"30b7fd76db21103356bd76c8d326cfcea41ebda0","tid":186561,"uid":102056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T09:48:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2c72f691f8e947d22b5bc5aef47ba02edcdcc51f","tid":186561,"uid":28913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T10:16:26.000Z","msg":"華人女人真係天生做雞"},{"pid":"4536772c289c20e5143b8f44b6fa37b1c0437bac","tid":186561,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T11:06:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b1d3bb59831a2d3f813834e4a35109b2d0d7331","tid":186561,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T13:15:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67325ca239cd5953681c8d39dc3879fa3d70c9ea","tid":186561,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T20:18:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c574d0700c4b0a96a51bb9358ceb5ff2f043af1","tid":186561,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T21:09:50.000Z","msg":"助養啫，使乜咁緊張"},{"pid":"dbdf53d55e3eca12c4f2a8addb8694abca700677","tid":186561,"uid":16250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T21:53:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁撚平既"}]}